---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dumpster Machine | America's Straight-Shooting Dumpster Rental">
	<main>
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="bg-slate-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-36">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598514982205-f36b96d1e8d4?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tighter uppercase text-white">
					No Hidden Fees. <br class="hidden md:block"/>
					<span class="text-amber-500">No Bullshit.</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-slate-300 font-medium">
					We team up with the best independent haulers in your city. They drive the trucks; we handle the logistics. You get local muscle with national-level accountability.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
					<a href="#quote" class="bg-amber-500 text-slate-900 font-black text-xl px-10 py-5 rounded-sm shadow-[6px_6px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:translate-x-[4px] transition-all uppercase tracking-wider block sm:inline-block">
						Find My City & Price
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Guarantees Section -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase text-slate-900 tracking-tight">How We Actually Work</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mt-4 font-medium">We do what we say we're going to do. Period.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<!-- Guarantee 1 -->
					<div class="bg-white p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(245,158,11,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-900 text-amber-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black mb-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">1</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900">The $50 On-Time Guarantee</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							If we don't deliver on the day we agreed to, we refund you $50. Period. And we will never leave you hanging for two business days. We put our money where our mouth is.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Guarantee 2 -->
					<div class="bg-white p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(245,158,11,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-900 text-amber-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black mb-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">2</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900">Pass-Through Only Philosophy</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							If the landfill doesn't charge us, we don't charge you. Sometimes an item slips in. If the landfill lets it slide, we let it slide. We never mark up or invent "processing" fees to make an extra buck off a mistake.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Guarantee 3 -->
					<div class="bg-white p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(245,158,11,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-900 text-amber-500 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black mb-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">3</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900">Free Early Delivery</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							We never promise exact delivery times because traffic is out of our control. Instead, schedule your delivery for the day before your project starts, and we will give you that extra day for FREE. Zero waiting around.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The Pitch Section -->
		<section class="py-24 bg-amber-500 border-y-8 border-slate-900">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="bg-slate-900 p-12 shadow-[12px_12px_0px_rgba(255,255,255,1)] border-4 border-white rounded-sm text-white">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase mb-6 text-amber-500">We Aren't the Cheapest in Town.</h2>
					<p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium text-slate-200">
						And we don't work with fly-by-night contractors who cut corners and don't carry insurance.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
						We are fully insured and do things by the book, because protecting your driveway and your property isn't worth risking over 50 bucks. You don't fight with independent drivers—we do. We run the logistics, manage the chaos, and ensure your box gets dropped exactly when you need it.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
